{"tid":1337030,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★62歲伯伯死去兩個月全屋蛆蟲，死者對股票很有研究，財產亦不少","createTime":"2019-07-21T07:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:22:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5f1832a55525e06f68aceb1f66e0af48e4be94","tid":1337030,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"工作人員發現死者對股票市場很有研究，財產亦不少，單單一本銀行存摺，就發現有12萬美元（約94萬港元）、還有極大袋硬幣。除了遺產，又發現一些家人、嬰兒的照片，更特別的是死者有很多封信件，都寫著「請聯絡我」。工作人員相信，死者性格較為孤僻，不喜歡聯絡他人。<br />\n<br />\n第2個個案<br />\n<br />\n第2宗個案更嚴重，62歲的死者在家裏孤獨死後2個月才比發現，導致屍身已經腐爛只剩下骨頭。工作人員處理現場前，先到訪了死者的鄰居了解情況。鄰居指，家裏傳出難聞的氣味，近一星期更不斷有蒼蠅飛入屋，自己都殺了無數隻蒼蠅了。她又透露，死者身體長年都很弱，不便於行，5年來生活於沒有水、電、煤的家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2400000/2403947/clean_thumb_20190717_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2400000%2F2403947%2Fclean_thumb_20190717_ch_1024.jpg&h=5320f61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2403947/%E3%80%90%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E3%80%91%E8%B5%B0%E9%80%B2%E5%AD%A4%E7%8D%A8%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6%E3%80%8062%E6%AD%B2%E4%BC%AF%E4%BC%AF%E6%AD%BB%E5%8E%BB%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%8B%E4%BD%88%E6%BB%BF%E6%B4%BB%E8%9B%86%E8%92%BC%E8%A0%85%E3%80%90%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%E3%80%91?mtc=10001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2403947%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E7%258D%25A8%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E3%2580%258062%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B1%258B%25E4%25BD%2588%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%259B%2586%25E8%2592%25BC%25E8%25A0%2585%25E3%2580%2590%25E